---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Affiliate Disclosure | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Advanced AI affiliate disclosure and FTC compliance information." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="disclosure-content">
				<h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
				<p><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

				<p>
					Advanced AI (advancedai.com) is a participant in various affiliate advertising programs designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to third-party products and services.
				</p>

				<h2>How It Works</h2>
				<p>
					Some of the links on this website are "affiliate links." This means if you click on the link and purchase an item or sign up for a service, Advanced AI will receive an affiliate commission. We only recommend products and services that we have personally evaluated or believe will add value to our readers.
				</p>

				<h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
				<p>
					In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC) guidelines on endorsements and testimonials, we disclose the following:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>We may receive compensation for links, reviews, and recommendations on this website.</li>
					<li>Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content or reviews.</li>
					<li>We strive to provide accurate and honest information in all of our content.</li>
					<li>Product or service availability, pricing, and offers may change after publication.</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Your Trust Matters</h2>
				<p>
					Our reputation and your trust are more important than any commission. If we recommend something, it's because we genuinely believe it's useful. If a product doesn't meet our standards, we won't recommend it regardless of any potential commission.
				</p>

				<h2>Questions?</h2>
				<p>
					If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure, please contact us at <strong>hello@advancedai.com</strong>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.disclosure-content {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.disclosure-content h2 {
		margin-top: 2em;
	}
	.disclosure-content ul {
		padding-left: 1.5em;
	}
	.disclosure-content li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
</style>
